<br>
While yes, there may be an efficient curve, there may also be alternate curves that do just as well. Try all mage groups with chain casting pets. Throw a Shammy in there into the mix. Is that &quot;more efficient&quot; or &quot;less efficient&quot;? To me, pre-PoP, it was more efficient. With our new pets, is it really that much of a drop in ability that our pets can no longer tank slowed mobs? Oh, so you don't want a Shaman? Too common? Recruit a beastlord, give them something to do. Heck, get a bard to pull for you. Heck, run without, see how bad it is!<br>
